# Vue Frontend Conventions

- Use `<script setup lang="ts">` at the top of the file.
- Put the `<template>` section after the script block.
- Keep styling in the shared `src/front-end/styles/` tree instead of local SFC style blocks unless there is a strong reason not to.
- Match existing editor and motion-inspector patterns before inventing new component structures.
- If a new frontend feature needs HTTP requests, prefer Axios over `fetch` and add it intentionally.
